      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready to go and runs like a dream! I\u2019m looking for someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. It's super reliable and looking for its next adventure\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
